{"tid":1871381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係同性戀 早排去旅行揼骨...","createTime":"2020-02-09T11:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T04:19:48.000Z","uid":164163,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5de89b62b89ec759b314e290aa95f8f1813904e0","tid":1871381,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"咁我就同一個女仔fd（姊妹）去揼骨啦<br />\n一入到去 好多揼骨師傅都係當地後生女 <br />\n突然間我個fd 就喺我耳邊講<br />\n<br />\n👨🏻(我)<br />\n👩🏻(fd)<br />\n<br />\n👩🏻: 2點鐘方向 啱啱嗰條女見到你就嘩咗一聲<br />\n👨🏻: 梗係啦 咁我都知自己個樣咩事嘅😅😅<br />\n👩🏻:Noooo 佢嗰個樣係見到你好似執到寶咁 嗱嗱嗱 佢而家仲定定望緊你<br />\n<br />\n之後我就望過去 個fd又好似講得幾中咁 佢一見到我望佢 就即刻衝咗入房準備架生<br />\n<br />\n咁跟住我同個fd就分房揼骨 因為性別關係 之後 居然係啱啱嗰條女幫我揼骨 🙄😅<br />\n<br />\n咁其實嗰個揼骨妹師傅想點啊？"},{"pid":"2e6ea825882780c77de679d26e5f1f34a7b086db","tid":1871381,"uid":15605,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"個揼骨妹見你樣衰想揼鳩你"},{"pid":"ffbb8ffec872f6d4e15de13043cbf4c357347cf0","tid":1871381,"uid":198952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"揼邪骨？"},{"pid":"3fa21db346c68abc942b0d8312e9f7c35c07e054","tid":1871381,"uid":108756,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"成篇文其實想講咩？"},{"pid":"e681a68266d72653372d5ab6d5ed3cfda3fc8cc2","tid":1871381,"uid":123848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"唔去搵男技師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d9a767110a32d4b25aabe58111b7782b9c4090","tid":1871381,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6ea825882780c77de679d26e5f1f34a7b086db","tid":1871381,"uid":15605,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"個揼骨妹見你樣衰想揼鳩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"我梗係知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src